														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1216525">
									

<p>Just because it's not a rule doesn't mean it's not something we want people aware of.</p>
<p>We want people to know that we've seen a lot of these. Tread carefully, the terrain is treacherous and littered with the remains of your predecessors. Enter at your own risk. People should know these are the sort of concepts that need to work harder to stand out. It is not meant to suggest that people <em>cannot</em> try these. They are not forbidden. That's part of the reason they're written the way they are. We don't want them taken too seriously. We just want people to know that they need to be careful.</p>

							</div>

								
					
